          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CHSEP",
                "INTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Sample was irradiated in the MTR for six",
                "weeks and change in Cm245 contents was measured.",
                "Alpha-pulse analysis of curium sample showed a rather",
                "broad alpha peak with energy of about 5.4 MeV due to",
                "Cm245 and Cm245. The ratios of the 5.4-MeV alpha",
                "particles (Cm245 and Cm246) to spontaneous fission",
                "disintegrations were (5.8+-0.3)x10**3 and (2.7+-0.1)",
                "x10**3, respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
