              "free_text": [
                " The curium produced by the irradiation",
                "of two plutonium samples (total integrated fluxes",
                "4x10**21 and 8x10**21 neutrons) in the Materials",
                "Testing Reactor (MTR) was chemically purified from",
                "fission products and other actinide elements. The",
                "curium samples were analyzed in a 12-in., 60 degree",
                "mass spectrometer with a multiple filament source."
